data.description: CALLING ALL INVESTORS! Classic Victorian in the heart of old Delaware with much of its original charm, intact, and in good condition! With fantastic curb appeal, original hardwood, a massive bathroom that could be split into 2, a unique lofted owner's suite, and a large 3 season room, this home has so much potential! Only half a mile from Ohio Wesleyan University, directly next to Blue Limestone Park, and Hidden Valley Golf Course, the location could not be more ideal for an investment property. HVAC and Water Heater (2019), updated 200 amp electric in '16 and replaced panel. Selling AS IS.So much potential, see A2A's for more info!
